 Davido’s logistics manager, Isreal DMW has revealed why Zlatan blocked and denied knowing DJ Cuppy in public even though they have a song together. According to Isreal, DJ Cuppy is a very fake friend who mafia Zlatan Ibile after their hit song by keeping all the money they made from the song and not giving him a single cent. He also disclosed that Cuppy didn’t take care of Zlatan when she invited him to her fundraising for her foundation and didn’t even give him anything that Zlatan had to pay for his own hotel. Isreal then said Zlatan Ibile is just being himself as he can’t pretend to be happy when he isn’t hence the reason why he blocked Cuppy and also denied knowing her in public. Screenshot below; 